{"tid":1663424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"彥霖單野，可以繞過死因庭","createTime":"2019-10-19T11:44:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T12:21:27.000Z","uid":306880,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ce4e52a7a12da353b259a0bc2213b740ae51a112","tid":1663424,"uid":306880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:44:26.000Z","msg":"問左相熟殯儀鋪，如果緊急情況可唔可以繞過死因庭，佢話可以，要家屬去警處申請，申請Form8「搬移及埋葬屍體許可證」，但就要搵殯儀鋪處理及火化屍體。<br />\n大家唔好再瞄住死因庭，因為真係可以繞過，但大家可以搵下邊間殯儀鋪做左單火化，可以問佢地員工彥霖個時狀況。"},{"pid":"04bb06232cf4d5c0f18928b2d2f6e71703773d96","tid":1663424,"uid":172497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:45:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c14765f5c6e6774cac72fa601472793e2172b1c1","tid":1663424,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:45:45.000Z","msg":"[1020 行動Post] 香港人真係好痴線！不論組織力、耐力、創意玩到咁！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eovgRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eovgRS</a>"},{"pid":"12daedd6a2b8ac1687ea8f2e124c15297e66533d","tid":1663424,"uid":106050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:46:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">片中證人子明指出受陳彥霖舅父，母親委託尋人(母親聲稱女兒身體良好，無可能自殺)，但舅父(紅van司機)同母親同由30號起失蹤，子明已經搵人係舅父工作地點，屋企附近等左4日都無消息</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/97wdulhzWTk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F97wdulhzWTk&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoKhYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=fd0cbfdb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/97wdulhzWTk</a>"},{"pid":"747ecc23c0551c90f37bebae1c152d82cc4cc44d","tid":1663424,"uid":136727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:47:45.000Z","msg":"屌你老母!!! 所有和理非同文宣用我入嚟!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eovCES\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eovCES</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=